::'''Mydei:''' I rarely use it for cooking
::'''Mydei:''' Or I could go get some meat that's been stored for over ten years
::'''Mydei:''' That smell will definitely haunt you forever
:'''Mydei:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 21 Mydei 02.png|80px]]
:'''Mydei:''' There's a popular saying in Castrum Kremnos: "A soldier who wishes to become a General must first be an excellent chef"
